    <h2>Our goal is to become the world’s first global energy-efficiency company</h2>
    <h3>And we’re well on our way to achieving it!</h3>

    <div class="large-text space-bottom">

        <p>We signed our first client in 2007 while sitting at a rented desk in San Francisco. Since then, we’ve grown into a well-capitalized business serving 50 utilities—including 8 of the US’s 10 largest. Our product now reaches nearly 10 million homes in North America.</p>

        <p>Together with our clients and their customers, we’re saving energy, saving them money, and directly helping to reduce global carbon emissions. And our positive impact increases every single day. </p>
    
