    <h4><span class="highlight">Our Future</span></h4>
        
    <p>Energy efficiency is one of the world’s greatest untapped sources for emissions reductions. Whether you’re diagnosing factors behind a high utility bill, making use of a new smart meter, choosing a water heater, or sharing energy tips online, OPOWER wants to be there, offering immediate solutions for reducing the way you and those around you use energy. Our future growth is only limited by the number of extraordinary people we can find to help us think up new and greater ways to help people around the world consume energy more efficiently. We’d love to hear from you.</p>

